WEBVTT

1
00:14:56.886 --> 00:14:59.026 
我可是已婚男人了
Hey, married man over here.

2
00:14:59.026 --> 00:15:00.636 
是啊  更像是半个男人
Yeah, more like half a man.

3
00:15:00.806 --> 00:15:02.326 
好了  美女们  该上班了
All right, ladies, time to punch in.

4
00:15:02.326 --> 00:15:03.026 
走吧
Let's go.

5
00:15:04.656 --> 00:15:05.906 
你以前干什么的  约翰
So what's your story, John?

6
00:15:06.116 --> 00:15:08.076 
在别的地方做过保安吗
You ever been a security guard anywhere else?

7
00:15:08.076 --> 00:15:09.816 
-偶尔  -商场保安吗
- Here and there. - Mall cop?

8
00:15:10.166 --> 00:15:11.446 
超市保安吗
Supermarket stiff?

9
00:15:11.746 --> 00:15:13.116 
差不多吧
Something like that.

10
00:15:13.116 --> 00:15:15.506 
我只是想说  这儿可不是沃尔玛
All I'm saying is, this ain't Walmart.

11
00:15:15.766 --> 00:15:17.446 
你之前被抢过吗
You ever been robbed before?

12
00:15:17.446 --> 00:15:18.516 
就一次
Once.

13
00:15:19.426 --> 00:15:21.436 
我和我搭档在转移一台自动取款机里的钱
My partner and I were servicing this ATM.

14
00:15:21.586 --> 00:15:23.206 
两个人带着枪出现
These two guys came up with guns.

15
00:15:23.206 --> 00:15:25.756 
我想当英雄来着  穿着防弹背心中了两枪
I tried to be a hero. Took two in the vest.

